quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,1,"They will ask you about booty. Say: ´Booty belongs to Allah and the Messenger. So have taqwa of Allah and put things right between you. Obey Allah and His Messenger if you are muminun.´"
  8,2,"The muminun are those whose hearts tremble when Allah is mentioned, whose iman is increased when His Signs are recited to them, and who put their trust in their Lord"
  8,3,those who establish salat and give of what We have provided for them
  8,4,They are in truth the muminun. They have high ranks with their Lord and forgiveness and generous provision
  8,5,"Just as your Lord brought you out from your house with truth, even though a group of the muminun disliked it"
  8,6,arguing with you about the Truth after it had been made clear as though they were being driven to their death with open eyes
  8,7,"When Allah promised you that one of the two parties would be yours and you would have liked it to have been the unarmed one, whereas Allah desired to verify the Truth by His words and to cut off the last remnant of the kafirun"
  8,8,"This was so that He might verify the Truth and nullify the false, even though the evildoers hate that"